(ns cxl_memory.actor
  "cxl_memory clean-room actor — Clojure over the kotoba Datom log (EAVT, Datomic-isomorphic,
  ADR-2605262130 + ADR-2605312345). CXL memory pooling / expansion fabric.

  Generated by 70-tools/scaffold_wave11_clj_datomic.py — replaces the Python main.py.
  CRUD + validation over a DI `DatomPort` seam (no external managed DB; the production
  adapter is kotoba-kqe, the test/browser adapter is `in-memory-datom`). No proprietary code."
  (:require [clojure.string :as str]))

